document_data.mainbody:
'''''Manual of the Planes 1st edition''''' is a 1{{st}}-edition ''Advanced Dungeons & Dragons'' accessory. 
{{quote|''...from [[Arcadia]] to [[Pandemonium]], from the plane of elemental [[Elemental Plane of Fire|Fire]] to the [[Astral plane]], vast new worlds of adventure are now open to players.''

''A vital source book for players and DMs of all levels of experience, the ''Manual of the Planes'' details the manifold worlds of the known planes of existence. This book describes the inhabitants, rulers, and environments of these worlds, as well as rules for movement, survival, combat, and spell use in these alien surroundings. A different style of AD&D<sup>&reg;</sup> adventures awaits!''
}}
